<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="H" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Heed2" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Heed,</orth> vb. 1) to attend to: <cit><quote>you must be so too, if h. me,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tmp 2.1.220" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. II, 1, 220</bibl></cit>. 2) to keep with care, to look after: <emph>it</emph> (the snake) <cit><quote>shall be --ed,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ant 5.2.269" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. V, 2, 269</bibl></cit>.
